    • Constructor Detail

      • PathGenerator

        public PathGenerator(double fwdMaxVel,
                     @Nullable
                     @Nullable java.lang.Double revMaxVel,
                     double maxAccel,
                     @Nullable
                     @Nullable java.lang.Double deltaTimeSecs)
        Default constructor.
        Parameters:
        fwdMaxVel - The maximum speed for the profile to reach going forwards, in feet/sec.
        revMaxVel - The maximum speed (not velocity, this should be positive) for the profile to reach going in reverse, in feet/sec. Defaults to fwdMaxVel.
        maxAccel - The maximum acceleration for the profile to reach, in feet/(sec^2)
        deltaTimeSecs - The amount of time between each point, in seconds. Defaults to .02 seconds, or 20 milliseconds.

                                         double currentVel,
                                         double currentAccel,
                                         double destinationPos)
        Generate a profile given the current state and desired end state.
        Parameters:
        currentPos - The current position in feet.
        currentVel - The current velocity in feet/sec.
        currentAccel - The current acceleration in feet/(sec^2).
        destinationPos - The desired position in feet.
        Returns:
        A motion profile that will move from the current state to the destination.
